		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Brix Battle brix batle birx bltaeieoijadpoisfvsd<br /><br />Game updated!<br /><strong>It's the same game with more levels, more balls per continue and unbugged paddle!</strong><br /><br /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/nYGbz8T.gif" alt="Image" /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/MqONUAo.gif" alt="Image" /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/wuYqVWc.gif" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Can you beat all 10 levels?<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level1_Spiral<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level2_Teeth<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level3_Cuteface<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level4_1stMetal<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level5_Pillbox<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level6_Pachinko<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level7_NES<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level8_Vase<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level9_Factory<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw Match_Level10_Fort</div><br /><br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Name:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Brick Breaker<br /><br />Submitted By:&nbsp; &nbsp; Punch<br /><br />Category:&nbsp; &nbsp;Category 1<br /><br />Description:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;You are a cute unidentified lifeform that, for some reason, has to break walls of different layouts.<br /><br />Controls:&nbsp; &nbsp;D-pad: Movement<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;B: Hasten movement<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A: Hold to aim, release to fire a ball.<br /><br />Rom info:&nbsp; &nbsp;Mapper 0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;24 KB (16k prog + 8k char)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1P controller required<br /><br />Credits:&nbsp; &nbsp;Punch - Everything else except for...<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CongusBongus - Ingame Music<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Shiru - FamiTone2 music engine<br /><br />Other:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; This has 10 levels total. When you run out of time, you can continue where you left if you have more than 1 ball.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;When losing all balls, your game will be over, however you can continue from the start of the level if you have<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;enough credits.</div>

		
